        Selling in Wakerley 2026
      </h1>
      <p style="font-size:1rem;color:rgba(240,236,228,0.6);line-height:1.8;max-width:54ch;">
        Wakerley's modern executive estates, larger family blocks and bayside-reach lifestyle attract a deliberate family buyer from across the inner east and the eastern corridor. Here is what sellers need to know in 2026.
      </p>
